### Tests HTTP directs sur les deux instances InfluxDB 3 Core du projet.
### A utiliser avec l'extension VSCode "REST Client" (humao.rest-client) :
### ouvrir ce fichier, cliquer sur "Send Request" au-dessus de chaque bloc.
###
### Ces valeurs correspondent aux defauts de .env.example. Si vous avez
### change le port/token dans votre .env, mettez a jour les variables ici.

@live_host = localhost
@live_port = 8183
@live_token = apiv3_mspr2-live-dev-token
@live_db = sensor_live

@staging_host = localhost
@staging_port = 8182
@staging_token = apiv3_mspr2-staging-dev-token
@staging_db = sensor_staging

###############################################################################
# LIVE (mspr2-influxdb-live)
###############################################################################

### Live - healthcheck (pas d'auth requise)
GET http://{{live_host}}:{{live_port}}/health

### Live - lister les tables (verifie le token + l'existence de la base)
POST http://{{live_host}}:{{live_port}}/api/v3/query_sql
Authorization: Bearer {{live_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "db": "{{live_db}}",
  "q": "SHOW TABLES"
}

### Live - ecrire un point de test (line protocol, precision secondes)
POST http://{{live_host}}:{{live_port}}/api/v3/write_lp?db={{live_db}}&precision=s
Authorization: Bearer {{live_token}}
Content-Type: text/plain

sensor_data,id_machine=test,sensor=test value=42 {{$timestamp}}

### Live - relire les 5 derniers points de sensor_data
POST http://{{live_host}}:{{live_port}}/api/v3/query_sql
Authorization: Bearer {{live_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "db": "{{live_db}}",
  "q": "SELECT * FROM sensor_data ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 5"
}

### Live - sans token (doit repondre 401)
POST http://{{live_host}}:{{live_port}}/api/v3/query_sql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "db": "{{live_db}}",
  "q": "SHOW TABLES"
}

###############################################################################
# STAGING (mspr2-influxdb-staging)
###############################################################################

### Staging - healthcheck (pas d'auth requise)
GET http://{{staging_host}}:{{staging_port}}/health

### Staging - lister les tables
POST http://{{staging_host}}:{{staging_port}}/api/v3/query_sql
Authorization: Bearer {{staging_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "db": "{{staging_db}}",
  "q": "SHOW TABLES"
}

### Staging - relire les 5 derniers points de sensor_data (alimente par Telegraf)
POST http://{{staging_host}}:{{staging_port}}/api/v3/query_sql
Authorization: Bearer {{staging_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "db": "{{staging_db}}",
  "q": "SELECT * FROM sensor_data ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 5"
}

### Staging - sans token (doit repondre 401)
POST http://{{staging_host}}:{{staging_port}}/api/v3/query_sql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "db": "{{staging_db}}",
  "q": "SHOW TABLES"
}
